SELECT [b].[Price], [b].[KoltukNumarası], [o].[Fiyat], [p].[Name], [p0].[Name], [o].[Tarih], [h].[Surname], [h].[Cinsiyet], [h].[Name], [b].[SeferNumara]

INNER JOIN [Provinces] AS [p] ON [r].[GidisId] = [p].[Id]
